{"type":"message","id":"321f96a5","parentId":"e582c2d4","timestamp":"2026-03-26T11:23:28.424Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"监控模式已启用，但建议先杀死干扰进程。不过，可以先扫描看看。接口可能命名为 wlan1mon。检查接口列表。使用 ip link show。但先继续扫描目标 WiFi。\n\n使用 airodump-ng wlan1mon 扫描。但 airodump-ng 需要运行一段时间来收集信息。我们可以运行一段时间（比如 10 秒）然后终止。使用 timeout 命令。\n\n执行：timeout 10s sudo airodump-ng wlan1mon。使用 echo 传递密码。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_yy3BVD13W5ws3zGJ20FVRF0J","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"666\" | sudo -S timeout 10 airodump-ng wlan1mon 2>&1 | head -50"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":324,"output":292,"cacheRead":18816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19432,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774524201173,"responseId":"028855ca-1cf7-4a13-b625-7854640f3ec4"}}
