{"type":"message","id":"4575cdca","parentId":"19b1d642","timestamp":"2026-03-26T11:23:34.587Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"接口名称不对。监控模式启用后，接口名可能是 mon0 或其他。检查 airmon-ng 输出：显示 monitor mode enabled，但没有给出新接口名。通常会是 wlan1mon。但可能没有创建成功，因为干扰进程。\n\n运行 airmon-ng check kill 杀死进程，然后重试。先杀死干扰进程。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Oe6K00SoXzQYuvUQDsUfxBS8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"666\" | sudo -S airmon-ng check kill 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":245,"output":206,"cacheRead":19136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19587,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774524208620,"responseId":"27d6ad73-1269-45c6-9b08-805c7e16c602"}}
